export const listOfQuizes=[
    {name: "Nintendo quiz",
        id:1,
        questions: [
        {
        rightAnswerId : 2,
          question: 'Who is the face of nintedo?',
          id: 1,
          answers: [
            {text:`Sonic`,id:1},
            {text:`Mario`,id:2},
            {text:`Kirby`,id:3},
            {text:`Link`,id:4}]
        
      },{
        rightAnswerId : 1,
        
          question: 'Which nintendo game involes fighting and nintendo characters?',
          id: 2,
          answers: [
            {text:`Super Smash Bros`,id:1},
            {text:`Dave guy`,id:2},
            {text:`Cars 2`,id:3},
            {text:`sonic free riders`,id:4}]
        
      },{
        rightAnswerId : 1,
        
          question: 'Who is Nintendos main rival?',
          id: 3,
          answers: [
            {text:`Sega`,id:1},
            {text:`Microsoft`,id:2},
            {text:`Sony`,id:3},
            {text:`The founder`,id:4}]
        
      },{
        rightAnswerId : 4,
        
          question: 'What was the name of Nintendo\'s least successful home console?',
          id: 4,
          answers: [
            {text:`The Game Boy`,id:1},
            {text:`The Megadrive`,id:2},
            {text:`The WII U`,id:3},
            {text:`The Virtual Boy`,id:4}]
        
      },
      {
        rightAnswerId : 4,
        
          question: 'Which of the following is NOT a kirby game?',
          id: 5,
          answers: [
            {text:`Kirby Tilt'n Tumble`,id:1},
            {text:`Kirby and The Fighters`,id:2},
            {text:`Kirby Air Ride`,id:3},
            {text:`Kirby Battle!`,id:4}]
        
      },
      {
        rightAnswerId : 4,
        
          question: 'How long had Nintendo wanted Yoshi to be in the Mario series?',
          id: 6,
          answers: [
            {text:`Since Donkey Kong`,id:1},
            {text:`Since Mario 3`,id:2},
            {text:`Since early development of Super Mario World`,id:3},
            {text:`Since Super Mario Brothers`,id:4}]
        
      },
    ] 

    },
    {
      name: `Video Games Trivia`,
      id: 2,
      question: [
        {
          rightAnswerId : 2,
            question: ' What was the name of the videogame designer who created the Mario, The Legend of Zelda, and Star Fox franchises?',
            id: 1,
            answers: [
              {text:`Mario Linguini`,id:1},
              {text:`Shigeru Miyamoto`,id:2},
              {text:`Fusajiro Yamauchi`,id:3},
              {text:`Ken Kutaragi`,id:4}]
          
        },
        {
          rightAnswerId : 2,
            question: 'What is the setting/era of the original Call of Duty?',
            id: 2,
            answers: [
              {text:`WW1`,id:1},
              {text:`WW2`,id:2},
              {text:`WW3`,id:3},
              {text:`The Cold War`,id:4}]
          
        },
        {
          rightAnswerId : 1,
            question: 'What classic video game did Tony Stark catch a member of S.H.I.E.L.D. playing in the first Avengers movie?',
            id: 3,
            answers: [
              {text:`Galaga`,id:1},
              {text:`Pac-Man`,id:2},
              {text:`Mortal Kombat`,id:3},
              {text:`Frogger`,id:4}]
          
        },
        {
          rightAnswerId : 3,
            question: 'Which video game holds the record for having the highest budget to ever produce?',
            id: 4,
            answers: [
              {text:`Halo 5: Guardians`,id:1},
              {text:`Call of Duty: Black Ops III`,id:2},
              {text:`Grand Theft Auto V`,id:3},
              {text:`Guitar Hero`,id:4}]
          
        },
        {
          rightAnswerId : 3,
            question: 'What are the professions of Mario and Luigi?',
            id: 5,
            answers: [
              {text:`Chefs`,id:1},
              {text:`Plumbers`,id:2},
              {text:`Grand Theft Auto V`,id:3},
              {text:`Guitar Hero`,id:4}]
          
        },
      ]
    }
    
    ]
